snippet.title: Merlin's Chess | Pre-Order Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the world of Merlin's Chess, where strategy meets magic!

Merlin's Chess is a fantasy-themed VR chess game brings a completely new gameplay experience to the greatest strategy game ever. Explore an immersive and enchanting way to play chess.

Now Available for Pre-Order!
Pre-Order Now: https://vr.meta.me/s/1L8CWqLJxzQCnfS
